JJ Valaya presented his collection titled 'Alma' at FDCI #ICW2022

The collection marked the celebration of 30 years of the label and takes inspiration from Spain.
Luxurious fabrics, elegant details, inspired prints and the designer’s timeless and much loved embroideries define this season’s Couture collection in all its glory as it transcends its journey blending the designer’s ethos with that of Spain.

• @kaaishabyshalini AFREEN:  SUMMER FESTIVE 2022

What makes a woman beautiful? Is it her looks, or her talent? Is it her strength of character, or her honesty? Is it her leadership, or her nurturing?

At Kaaisha, we believe that every woman is beautiful, and there is no singular definition of beauty. AFREEN, our Summer 2022 collection, celebrates the many facets of a woman. Today, women lead the world by example, and our collection is an ode to them.

The shades and layers of feminine beauty are reflected by the different sections of the collection - some strong and statement making, the others classical and delicate. A plethora of fabrics, colours and shapes cater to the needs of those seeking something experimental, but with a traditional core.

AFREEN is every woman.

latestPosts.caption:
Soul Uninterrupted

Through pain, poetry and performance, Navkirat Sodhi ( @thepoetresse ), tells her story of recovery and a love that dances along the way for @VogueIndia 

“And on days when the scars weigh heavy, I remind myself they’re love letters from life imprinted on me. A reminder that I’m precious to her. That nothing interrupts the soul.” - @thepoetresse

Navkirat is styled by ggpanther in custom Gaurav Gupta Couture. She wears:

‘Warrior Swan’, a sheer white tulle drape featuring a corset bodice with exposed boning, complemented by a long overlay that adds movement.

‘Spirit Armour’ a structured brocade corset featuring woven sacred chants and an exaggerated back panel for added dimension. The top is paired with a sheer black tulle wrap skirt. 

Photographer: Bhumika Sharma (@akimuhb_)
Stylist: Gaurav Gupta (ggpanther)
Words by: Navkirat Sodhi (@thepoetresse)
Hair and Makeup: Kaajee Rai (@kaajee_rai  @karanrai001 @kiran_chhetri92 )
Bookings Editor: Aliza Fatma (@alizaafatmaa)
Sr. Designer: Shagun Jangid (@shagun_jangid)
Assisted by: Aashima Chopra (@aashimaachopra), Anna Mehta (@annameht) (Bookings).

🎬✨ From Dreams to Runways – Kaajee Rai’s Journey to the Fashion & Makeup Industry!
Once a passionate learner within our academy walls, Kaajee Rai has now carved his path in the vibrant world of fashion and makeup. 💄 His creativity, dedication, and talent have taken him from student life to professional success — working on real-world sets and styling for the spotlight.

For every aspiring artist out there, his story is proof that with the right foundation, the sky’s the limit! 🚀
